                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "The bakery exceeded my expectations! The croissants were buttery and flaky, 
                                and the custom cake I ordered for my son's birthday was not only visually 
                                stunning but also incredibly delicious."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="testimonial__item">
                            <div class="testimonial__author">
                                <div class="testimonial__author__pic">
                                    <img src="/cake-main/img/testimonial/ta-2.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="testimonial__author__text">
                                    <h5>Jennifer Brown</h5>
                                    <span>Berlin</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
