                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "What a gem of a bakery! From the friendly staff to the wide array of pastries,
                                everything was top-notch. I will recommend this place to all of my friends and
                                will definitely visit again."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="testimonial__item">
                            <div class="testimonial__author">
                                <div class="testimonial__author__pic">
                                    <img src="/cake-main/img/testimonial/ta-1.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="testimonial__author__text">
                                    <h5>Anna Garcia</h5>
                                    <span>London</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="rating">
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "As a pastry connoisseur, I have high standards, and this bakery met them all.
                                The eclairs were a highlight - perfectly balanced flavors and a delicate texture.
                                I Highly recommend!"
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="testimonial__item">
                            <div class="testimonial__author">
                                <div class="testimonial__author__pic">
                                    <img src="/cake-main/img/testimonial/ta-2.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="testimonial__author__text">
                                    <h5>Emma Davis</h5>
                                    <span>Munich</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="rating">
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "The bakery's selection of vegan treats was impressive, and I appreciated
                                the creativity in their recipes. The vegan chocolate cake I tried was rich
                                and indulgent. I will try the Pancakes next time."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="testimonial__item">
                            <div class="testimonial__author">
                                <div class="testimonial__author__pic">
                                    <img src="/cake-main/img/testimonial/ta-1.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="testimonial__author__text">
                                    <h5>Ophelia Nunez</h5>
                                    <span>Berlin</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="rating">
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "The bakery's artisanal breads were exceptional, with a crusty exterior and a soft,
                                flavorful interior. The ambience was cozy, making it the perfect spot for a leisurely brunch."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="testimonial__item">
                            <div class="testimonial__author">
                                <div class="testimonial__author__pic">
                                    <img src="/cake-main/img/testimonial/ta-2.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="testimonial__author__text">
                                    <h5>Ava Wilson</h5>
                                    <span>Amsterdam</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="rating">
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star"></span>
                                <span class="icon_star-half_alt"></span>
                            </div>
                            <p>
                                "I was blown away by the attention to detail in every pastry I tried. The raspberry tart was a standout,
                                with a perfect balance of sweetness and tartness. Definitely a must-visit for any pastry lover!"
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Testimonial Section End -->
    <!-- Instagram Section Begin -->
    <section class="instagram spad">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 p-0">
                    <div class="instagram__text">
                        <div class="section-title">
                            <span>Follow us on instagram</span>
                            <h2>Sweet moments are saved as memories.</h2>
                        </div>
